# Excel Analysis Summary

## Dataset Overview
- Total Sessions: 12,000
- Plants: 5
- Devices: 20
- Analysis Period: Jan 2025 - Jan 2026

## Analysis Performed
- Data Cleaning & Validation
- Feature Engineering (3 new columns)
- 8 Pivot Table Analyses
- 7 Charts & Visualizations
- Interactive Dashboard

## Key Findings

### Plant Performance
- Bokaro has highest productivity score
- Vadodara has lowest productivity score

### Shift Analysis
- Night shift most productive
- Night shift has longest resolution time
- Morning shift has highest command failure rate

### Platform Comparison
- MS Teams outperforms Webex across all metrics
- 33% higher resolution efficiency
- 17% higher productivity score
- 15% higher command success rate

### Noise Impact
- High noise increases failure rate by 60%
- External microphone not effective
- Alternative solutions recommended

### Device Health
- All 20 devices at medium battery risk
- No devices at critical failure risk
- Preventive maintenance recommended

### Monthly Trends
- Session volume volatile month to month
- Productivity stable between 76-78%
- Jan 2026 data incomplete

## Recommendations
1. Investigate Vadodara plant performance
2. Optimize night shift resolution process
3. Standardize MS Teams across all plants
4. Restrict device usage in high noise areas
5. Schedule preventive maintenance for devices

